íŸ@4804c9f439f13a8c4f6f3ddf503383bc9d12e7398961200248062a74badd3a11⁄Title: title: debug env
Path: Examples
Content:
Get PATH variable that externals see.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> debug env | get PATH!


```
Create a .env file.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> debug env | transpose key value | each {$"($in.key)=($in.value | to json)"} | save .env


```
